data.description: Beautiful three bedroom 1.5 bath close to Beachwood Mall, Bexley Park, Euclid Creek, and Notre Dame College, near shopping and dining. Living room with fireplace is surrounded by built-ins. Large back yard with deck, patio, and privacy fence. Three car garage with workshop. Second workshop on the lower level of the house. Furnace from 2022, water tank 2019. Marble flooring in the bathroom new in 2023. Downstairs bath has shower, and new faucet with warranty.
